Openbox is a highly configurable, next generation window manager with extensive standards support. {{Package|x11-wm/openbox}} is actively maintained on Gentoo and you can install is as usual using:
{{Emerge|x11-xm/openbox}}

{{Note| This guide is not a replacement to the [http://www.gentoo.org/doc/en/openbox.xml official Gentoo Openbox Guide] at the moment. Its only purpose is to illustrate the changes between version 3.4 and 3.5 }}
