=== Icons in openbox menu ===
Since version 3.5.0 you can have icons next to your menu entries. For this:

1) You must emerge openbox with imlib support.
Add USE flag "imlib" for x11-wm/openbox into you /etc/portage/package.use like this:
"x11-wm/openbox imlib" and run "#emerge x11-wm/openbox"

2) Add <showIcons>yes</showIcons> in the <menu> section of the rc.xml file

3) Add in menu.xml icon="<path>" like this:
<pre>
<nowiki><menu label="Shells" icon="/usr/share/icons/shell.png">
	<item label="xterm" icon="/usr/share/icons/xterm.png"><action name="Execute">
		<execute>xterm</execute>
	</action></item></nowiki></pre>

